{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_12_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ロケ当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（無事、筆記試験が終わったようだな……）\n（次はついに実技か……）",
      "startTime": 5.8842466325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、また不安そうな顔して……\nもう、大丈夫ですよ、安心して下さい",
      "startTime": 12.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かに、操船練習では一度\n振り落とされちゃいましたけど……",
      "startTime": 20.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "最後はきっちり乗りこなしてたじゃないですか\nあの感覚はちゃんと体が覚えています",
      "startTime": 26.033335495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、こんなところで挫けていたら\nお姉ちゃんに胸を張れませんから",
      "startTime": 32.6000021617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.3338896000027,
          "startTime": 36.2333360513
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 37799.997838300005,
          "startTime": 70.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（本番前に琴乃はそう言っていた……）\n（だから俺はもう不安には思わないぞ、頑張れ、琴乃）",
      "startTime": 40.1338201674,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4799.5158839,
          "startTime": 44.9333360513
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watercraft-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5816.1798326,
          "startTime": 45.95
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（お、琴乃が水上バイクに乗って、エンジンをかけた！）\n（振り落とされないでバイクを操ってる！）",
      "startTime": 48.766669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ウォーン……\nウォンウォンウォーン……",
      "startTime": 53.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-04.m4a",
          "delay": 2766.668113100003,
          "startTime": 56.2666681131
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（おお……！！）\n（高波をものともしないで、海を滑るように走っていく！）",
      "startTime": 57.4666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ウォンウォンウォーン！！",
      "startTime": 61.4666681131,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-04.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.330281600004,
          "startTime": 64.1999983947
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（軽快にターンまで決めた！　格好いいぞ！）\n（体の一部のようにバイクを操ってるじゃないか！）",
      "startTime": 67.3666650136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（し、しかしずっと口で何か言ってるようにも）\n（見えるが……とにかくこれで合格間違いなしだ！）",
      "startTime": 73.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6633.333253899991,
          "startTime": 80.5333332539
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 40833.33333329999,
          "startTime": 114.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 76966.66666670001,
          "startTime": 150.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 113100,
          "startTime": 187
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 149233.3333333,
          "startTime": 223.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 183633.3333333,
          "startTime": 257.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-night",
      "startTime": 80.2833332539
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、今日はお疲れ様でしたー……\n付き添い、ありがとうございます……",
      "startTime": 86.2666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃こそお疲れ様。ロケ、大成功だったな\nスタッフさんも放送するのが楽しみだって喜んでいたよ",
      "startTime": 93.0999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "勉強や実技の練習を苦労してやった甲斐がありましたね\n……本番では、予想外のこともありましたけど",
      "startTime": 102.1666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "星見市がロケ地だったとはいえ\nまさかあんなに沢山の人が見学に来るなんて……",
      "startTime": 108.9333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに想像以上の人だかりだったな\n……だが、みんな、琴乃の姿に見惚れていたぞ",
      "startTime": 117.0333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、友達も見に来てたんですよね……\n可愛かったって言われて、さすがに照れちゃいました",
      "startTime": 126.561880121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ファンに見られるのとは、また違った感覚かもな\nそんな中でも、本当によく堂々と振る舞っていたよ",
      "startTime": 135.5333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "運転しているところは、本当に格好良かったぞ\n高波を掻き分けて進んでいく姿も素晴らしかった",
      "startTime": 143.3999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "そう、でしょうか……そう見えてました？\n私、ちゃんとやれてたかどうか、ちょっと不安で……",
      "startTime": 152.0333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何か不安だったのか？\n俺の方は、心配し過ぎなくらいだったが",
      "startTime": 159.3999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "実はこの衣装、雑誌で見たお姉ちゃんの水着に\nよく似てることに気付いちゃって……",
      "startTime": 166.9049884007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "それから、どうしても意識しちゃってたっていうか\n同じくらい堂々と出来てたのかなって、気になって",
      "startTime": 174.2999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、そう言われると、デザインが似ているな……\nでも、心配いらないよ。友達も褒めてくれたんだろ？",
      "startTime": 182.7013795153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "きっと麻奈も、見たらこう言うはずだ。「すっごく\n似合ってるよ。お揃いみたいで嬉しい！」って",
      "startTime": 190.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、確かに言いそうですね。ありがとうございます\nお揃いかぁ……お姉ちゃん、大袈裟なくらい喜びそう",
      "startTime": 202.5666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そういうのは分かるのに、なんでお姉ちゃんの\n気持ちは分からなかったんだろうなぁ……この人は",
      "startTime": 212.7333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　{user}さん……\n海、見て下さい、とっても綺麗ですよ",
      "startTime": 222.5333332857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "キラキラ光って……見惚れちゃいますね……\nやっぱり星見市の海は特別です……",
      "startTime": 232.5333301544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は昔、ここに一人で練習に来ていたよな\n夜に自主練していたのをよく覚えているよ",
      "startTime": 240.5666634877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_12_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしいですね。……月明かりが優しい夜の海は\n昼間とはまた違うことに気付かせてくれました",
      "startTime": 249.4333301544,
